m/apps/2231580/extras/52e493b4e933f729d2c60e6288e04b16.poster.avif?t=1722369616\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231580/extras/52e493b4e933f729d2c60e6288e04b16.webm?t=1722369616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231580/extras/52e493b4e933f729d2c60e6288e04b16.mp4?t=1722369616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Manage different types of drones for building walls and turrets, recharging capacitors, and harvesting resources to regain energy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231580/extras/7b1c39ba29bcf76d2f173fe512f8a299.poster.avif?t=1722369616\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231580/extras/7b1c39ba29bcf76d2f173fe512f8a299.webm?t=1722369616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231580/extras/7b1c39ba29bcf76d2f173fe512f8a299.mp4?t=1722369616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Buy new vehicles, turrets, and more.  Visit space stations to unlock upgrades.<br><br>See the <strong>Early Access</strong> section for more information.",
